title: Natural gas prices for households in Germany 2010 - 2018 , semi-annually
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Euro cents per kilowatt-hour. In total the number of data points it has is 17.
In general Euro cents per kilowatt-hour has rose over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2011_S1 and 2011_S2.
Maximum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour, about 6.89 was reported at Year 2013_S2
Minimum Euro cents per kilowatt-hour about 5.65 was reached at Year 2010_S1
